thread.title: Hundreds gather for Super Bowl Trump protest in Houston (VIDEOS, PHOTOS)
thread.title_full: Hundreds gather for Super Bowl Trump protest in Houston (VIDEOS, PHOTOS)

author: RT
title: Hundreds gather for Super Bowl Trump protest in Houston (VIDEOS, PHOTOS)
text:
— Houston DSA (@HoustonDSA) February 5, 2017 
Local TV station KHOU reported that activists from Black Lives Matter, the local Democratic Party, the American Civil Liberties Union (ACLU) and the Communist Party were all involved in the demonstration. Crowd gives an ovation to police standing by. Told "not to engage Trump supporters" if they're on the protest route. pic.twitter.com/CjreBqIe9l — Eric Adelson (@eric_adelson) February 5, 2017 
Placards criticizing Patriots’ star quarterback Tom Brady and head coach Bill Belichick, who have expressed support for Trump in the past, were evident amongst the crowd.
